Title: The death toll from flash floods in Morocco has risen to 37 after heavy rainfall wreaked havoc in southern and central parts of the country. Weather agencies have predicted more heavy rain in the country in the coming days. - News Arena India
Summary: The death toll from flash floods in Morocco has risen to 37 after heavy rainfall wreaked havoc in southern and central parts of the country. Weather agencies have predicted more heavy rain in the country in the coming days.  News Arena India
